# =============================================================================
# Mac mini legacy migration (Patrick 2026-07-17 14:57 MDT)
# =============================================================================
# During the Books v2 GitHub-first migration, the Mac mini working tree holds
# the v1 client surfaces as UNTRACKED files (rollback safety net for the
# `c834067` cleanup commit). These ignore rules prevent `git add -A` from
# accidentally staging them. Once the Mac mini working tree is renamed to
# task-manager-legacy-v1 and replaced with a fresh clone of GitHub, remove
# these rules and delete the legacy working tree.
#
# Tracking intent:
#   client/src/books/_archived/  → DELETED on GitHub at commit c834067
#   queued/TASK-completed-system-folder.md  → DELETED on GitHub at commit c834067
#   Both are kept on the Mac mini as untracked files for rollback reference.
client/src/books/_archived/
queued/TASK-completed-system-folder.md
# End legacy migration block — remove after fresh clone is in place.
